{
  "message": "\ud83d\udc1b Exclude .env from secret scanner + add test results\n\nThe secret scanner correctly detects secrets in .env, but .env is\ngitignored and expected to contain local secrets. Add .env patterns\nto the gitleaks allowlist so the scanner focuses on tracked files.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
